Yiyun Zhang(Benny)
yz523
CS275 - HW3

To run this project, type node app.js in the terminal and open the browser to the localhost:8080 page. The yz523_HW3.html page will show in the browser.
In the text field, you can enter a positive integer, and choose the drop down options to do the calculation: n factorial or summation series.
If the input is invalid, the corresponding hint will appear in the result division.
The result will received the calculation result from server and show in the result division.
To exit the program, press ctrl-c to stop the server and close the web browser.